title: 8.3.2.4.1 - Chlorofluorocarbons and hydrochlorofluorocarbons
section 8_3_2_4_1

  |The CFCs and HCFCs contribute approximately 11% of the {Topics.*The_Greenhouse_Effect WMGHG} {Topics.*Radiative_Forcing RF}. Although {Topics.*Emissions emissions} have been drastically reduced for CFCs, their long lifetimes mean that reductions take substantial time to affect their concentrations.


  

